query:
INSERT INTO wallet_activity (
                address, 
                first_activity_at, 
                last_activity_at, 
                activity_count
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $2, 1)
            ON CONFLICT (address) DO UPDATE SET
                last_activity_at = $2,
                activity_count = wallet_activity.activity_count + 1,
                updated_at = NOW()
